{"tid":595721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有個死蠢跌咗銀包。。。","createTime":"2018-03-17T02:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T10:09:24.000Z","uid":116509,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b30800d9d5f495c9afe4a088fcc36ed6403dc18b","tid":595721,"uid":116509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的， 有個笨蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跌咗銀包。 詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n昨日（16/3）6點半左右係中環至尖沙咀的天星小輪上跌咗一個啡色男裝銀包，內有身份証、八達通、恆生信用卡及提款卡，仲有幾張有紀念價值的相片，不捨得遺失<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位巴絲打可以幫小弟留意下<br />\n而且個銀包小弟用咗好多年，好有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n如有好心人執到，麻煩tg小弟(<a href=\"http://t.me/Fuyor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFuyor&d=adz%2BbpbjDbE0UrEjEAv%2BY8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=6f8a2e08\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/Fuyor</a>)或者交去差館，小弟真係感激不盡<br />\n<br />\n          <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab847c94b70fa4af7e6eff814dfa59c3aa4fde66","tid":595721,"uid":29523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"尖東又蝗又蝻，搵到都算奇蹟"},{"pid":"f806d4551b07ce4a4303b7c118d3ed03cbe09414","tid":595721,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"銀包入面居然無錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fa2fbecbf400d2ed57226685b617f8234ce9c9","tid":595721,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"r